      <h2 class="section3H">Publish biodiversity data</h2>
      <p class="section3">GBIF promotes and facilitates biodiversity data publishing by national institutions. It is possible to publish occurrence, sample-based or checklist data, using data standards and software adopted by GBIF. <br>GBIF Portugal provides support, training and infrastructure facilities for the uso of these tools.<br><br><a href="http://www.gbif.pt/taxonomy/term/29"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></span>Learn more</a>
      </p>
