      <h2 class="section3H">Using biodiversity data</h2>
      <p class="section3">See examples of using data published through GBIF. You can also reuse data in a portal or application, using the web services of the GBIF Portal and also from this national portal.
      <br><br><a href="https://www.gbif.org/resource/search?contentType=dataUse"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></span> See use examples</a>
